OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe renters scared of their
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdangerous homes            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Tenants who complain of dangerous or   
OL,6, potentially deadly faults in privately 
OL,7, rented homes are being let down by     
OL,8, councils, a BBC investigation suggests.
OL,10,FWhen landlords fail to fix hazards -   
OL,11,Fincluding serious faults that pose an  
OL,12,Fimmediate risk to health - councils in 
OL,13,FEngland have a legal duty to act.      
OL,15,FBut BBC News found the number of times 
OL,16,Fcouncils use enforcement powers is far 
OL,17,Flower than the number of reports made. 
OL,19,FThe LGA, representing councils, says   
OL,20,Fformal enforcement is a "last resort". 
